---
import "../styles/generel.css";
---

<section class="didyouknow-section" id="life-cycle-section">
  <div class="didyouknow-inner">
    <h1>DID YOU KNOW?</h1>

    <h3>Not all trash disappears the same way – or in the same time.</h3>

    <p>
      Explore how long it takes for everyday items to decompose, from plastic
      bottles to banana peels. The true “life cycle” of waste will help you
      understand why sorting and recycling matter. Because what you throw away
      today could still be here tomorrow.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .didyouknow-section {
    background-color: var(--green);
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--ashbrown);
    /* background-color: var(--light_green);  <- når du vil */
  }

  .didyouknow-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  h3 {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-family:
      lexend giga,
      sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--ashbrown);
  }
</style>
